[https://www.codenerve.com/beginner-java/lesson-5-methods/] on methods.

As you can see, this method takes in anint called grade and returns a String.
Which string depends on the grade parameters value. If the grade is greater or
equal to 40, then the if condition is true and it will execute the code inside
