String passOrFail = anotherIfStatement(10);
System.out.println(passOrFail);

[/vc_column_text][us_separator show_line=”1″ icon=”fas|code”][vc_column_text]If
… Else Statements
Ok, time for another conditional. This time, let’s look at the If .. Else
condition:

	private static String anIfElseStatement(int grade) {

		if (grade >=40){
			return "Congratulations you have passed the exam!";
